Tsubasa, here!

509
00:18:32,439 --> 00:18:34,328
Taro Misaki
now makes a very smart pass

510
00:18:34,353 --> 00:18:35,483
towards the penalty area.

511
00:18:38,483 --> 00:18:39,603
What a goal!

512
00:18:39,733 --> 00:18:42,523
Team Nankatsu is now
up by two goals to nothing.

513
00:18:42,767 --> 00:18:44,183
After the first goal,

514
00:18:44,208 --> 00:18:46,918
Team Nankatsu's been
revitalized.

515
00:18:48,403 --> 00:18:49,993
Tsubasa's incredible.

516
00:18:50,018 --> 00:18:52,518
Tell me, don't you think
he's fantastic?

517
00:18:52,933 --> 00:18:53,933
Yeah.

518
00:18:54,813 --> 00:18:56,893
I'm happy we came
all the way to Shizuoka

519
00:18:56,893 --> 00:18:57,893
to see him.

520
00:19:00,453 --> 00:19:02,833
MUSASHINO ELEMENTARY SCHOOL - TOKYO

521
00:19:03,313 --> 00:19:04,183
Yeah, you can do it!

522
00:19:04,313 --> 00:19:05,813
-Over here! Over here!
-Pass it, pass it!

523
00:19:05,933 --> 00:19:07,313
Hey, let's move already!

524
00:19:07,433 --> 00:19:08,933
Ugh, what a waste of time.

525
00:19:09,063 --> 00:19:10,063
He isn't here.

526
00:19:10,328 --> 00:19:11,748
Hey, Kojiro, tell me,

527
00:19:11,773 --> 00:19:13,273
who did we come see
at this school?

528
00:19:13,776 --> 00:19:15,776
I wanted to come see
two players...

529
00:19:15,801 --> 00:19:17,931
just before we played
our next match.

530
00:19:19,023 --> 00:19:21,183
One of them is
Genzo Wakabayashi,

531
00:19:21,313 --> 00:19:22,563
from Nankatsu.

532
00:19:22,983 --> 00:19:24,233
And the other player is...

533
00:19:24,258 --> 00:19:27,683
Jun Misugi from Musashi FC,
a high profile player.

534
00:19:27,708 --> 00:19:29,528
But neither of them is here
right now.

535
00:19:29,893 --> 00:19:31,733
I don't know Jun Misugi.

536
00:19:31,853 --> 00:19:33,273
You serious, Takeshi?

537
00:19:33,933 --> 00:19:35,933
They call him
the Prince of the Pitch.

538
00:19:35,933 --> 00:19:37,773
A very talented
young player.

539
00:19:37,893 --> 00:19:39,313
You can do it!

540
00:19:41,304 --> 00:19:43,158
And the ball
is in the clutches of

541
00:19:43,183 --> 00:19:45,603
Nankatsu's goalkeeper,
Genzo Wakabayashi.

542
00:19:45,628 --> 00:19:46,708
Despite his injury,

543
00:19:46,733 --> 00:19:48,103
Genzo is risking
everything

544
00:19:48,128 --> 00:19:49,095
to defend his goal.

545
00:19:49,120 --> 00:19:50,767
Nankatsu
can taste victory

546
00:19:50,792 --> 00:19:51,970
at the tip of
their tongue.

547
00:19:51,995 --> 00:19:53,365
There's only one minute
on the clock.

548
00:19:53,890 --> 00:19:56,050
Listen up, I want you
to give me another goal.

549
00:19:56,313 --> 00:19:57,523
Tsubasa!

550
00:19:57,945 --> 00:19:59,775
Genzo
passes the ball to Tsubasa,

551
00:19:59,800 --> 00:20:01,920
the star striker
of Nankatsu.

552
00:20:02,392 --> 00:20:04,353
Stop him.
Don't let him shoot.

553
00:20:06,256 --> 00:20:07,836
I know where
I need to shoot.

554
00:20:13,358 --> 00:20:14,558
Great goal!

555
00:20:14,583 --> 00:20:16,741
Tsubasa gets a hat trick!

556
00:20:18,733 --> 00:20:20,618
The referee signals
the end of the match.

557
00:20:20,643 --> 00:20:24,319
Team Nankatsu is
the champion of Shizuoka!

558
00:20:24,344 --> 00:20:25,683
Yeah, that's right!

559
00:20:25,708 --> 00:20:26,983
The team
that is going to represent

560
00:20:27,103 --> 00:20:29,233
our prefecture at
the national tournament

561
00:20:29,353 --> 00:20:30,683
-will be
-I'm so happy right now!

562
00:20:30,708 --> 00:20:31,958
-the Nankatsu squad.
-Me too.

563
00:20:32,103 --> 00:20:32,893
Until now,

564
00:20:32,893 --> 00:20:34,643
Tsubasa has made
three goals

565
00:20:34,773 --> 00:20:36,683
in every single match.

566
00:20:36,708 --> 00:20:38,975
He's a talent
we've never seen before.

567
00:20:39,000 --> 00:20:40,330
Incredible.

568
00:20:40,596 --> 00:20:41,908
You really are incredible.

569
00:20:41,933 --> 00:20:43,183
Job well done, Tsubasa.

570
00:20:43,408 --> 00:20:44,908
-Good job out there, guys!
-Great work, team!

571
00:20:44,933 --> 00:20:46,683
What a pity, they beat us.

572
00:20:46,708 --> 00:20:49,368
We couldn't defeat Tsubasa
or Genzo Wakabayashi.

573
00:20:49,393 --> 00:20:50,393
They're better.

574
00:20:50,523 --> 00:20:51,853
Yeah, tell us about it.

575
00:20:52,198 --> 00:20:53,908
We couldn't compete
on their level.

576
00:20:53,933 --> 00:20:55,183
They won fair and square.

577
00:20:56,342 --> 00:20:57,842
It was a good match, guys.

578
00:20:58,433 --> 00:20:59,983
Oh! Tsubasa!

579
00:21:00,063 --> 00:21:01,063
Huh?

580
00:21:01,186 --> 00:21:02,686
Go to the national
tournament...

581
00:21:02,711 --> 00:21:04,581
and you win it for
all of us, you got that?

582
00:21:05,553 --> 00:21:06,803
Thank you, Morimichi.

583
00:21:07,670 --> 00:21:08,670
Yeah!

584
00:21:08,783 --> 00:21:09,783
They really did it.

585
00:21:09,808 --> 00:21:10,888
Everything ended well.

586
00:21:11,104 --> 00:21:11,774
Yes.

587
00:21:12,144 --> 00:21:13,328
-Hey, Tsubasa!
-Hey, Tsubasa!

588
00:21:13,353 --> 00:21:15,563
-Congratulations on--
-Congratulations on winning!

589
00:21:15,792 --> 00:21:16,792
It's that brat again!

590
00:21:17,063 --> 00:21:17,983
You were great!

591
00:21:18,103 --> 00:21:20,183
I hope I see you at
the national tournament.

592
00:21:20,668 --> 00:21:22,288
I got transferred too,
you know?

593
00:21:22,313 --> 00:21:24,455
And now, I'm with
Team Musashi from Tokyo.

594
00:21:24,480 --> 00:21:26,276
I hope I see you very soon.

595
00:21:26,737 --> 00:21:28,737
Uh...
I think I know that player.

596
00:21:29,214 --> 00:21:30,384
You know him, Coach?

597
00:21:30,409 --> 00:21:31,459
Tell us who he is.

598
00:21:31,698 --> 00:21:32,998
His name's Jun Misugi.

599
00:21:33,354 --> 00:21:35,328
One of most talented
young players

600
00:21:35,353 --> 00:21:36,828
in the league right now.

601
00:21:36,853 --> 00:21:38,523
He's an exceptional player.

602
00:21:38,548 --> 00:21:39,918
Jun Misugi...

603
00:21:40,733 --> 00:21:41,853
You take care, Tsubasa.

604
00:21:43,014 --> 00:21:44,964
Who the hell does
she think she is?

605
00:21:45,502 --> 00:21:46,908
I guess I'll just
have to become

606
00:21:46,933 --> 00:21:48,328
the team's representative.

607
00:21:48,353 --> 00:21:49,853
-I'll be the manager.
-Huh?

608
00:21:49,933 --> 00:21:51,423
That way,
I'll be able to go to

609
00:21:51,448 --> 00:21:52,908
the national tournament
right next to

610
00:21:52,933 --> 00:21:54,363
-my handsome Tsubasa.
-Ugh...

611
00:21:54,373 --> 00:21:55,773
NATIONAL JUVENILE SOCCER TOURNAMENT SHIZUOKA REPRESENTATIVE NANKATSU SC CONGRATULATIONS!

612
00:21:55,773 --> 00:21:56,563
And so,

613
00:21:56,683 --> 00:21:57,846
the single elimination
tournament

614
00:21:57,871 --> 00:21:59,383
to choose Shizuoka
prefecture's team concluded.

615
00:21:59,408 --> 00:22:00,602
Leaving Nankatsu

616
00:22:00,627 --> 00:22:02,707
as the centerpiece
of all the matches.

617
00:22:04,563 --> 00:22:06,821
In the meantime,
the Wangan stadium,

618
00:22:06,846 --> 00:22:07,641
where the national
tournament matches

619
00:22:07,666 --> 00:22:09,368
will be held,

620
00:22:09,393 --> 00:22:11,328
anxiously awaits
the arrival of

621
00:22:11,353 --> 00:22:13,063
the new young players.

622
00:22:17,460 --> 00:22:19,080
You did it, Tsubasa.

623
00:22:19,490 --> 00:22:20,490
Yeah!

624
00:22:20,853 --> 00:22:22,853
The next step is
the national tournament.

625
00:22:23,023 --> 00:22:25,733
From now on, you'll have to
play seriously.

626
00:22:25,877 --> 00:22:26,877
Yeah.

627
00:22:27,257 --> 00:22:28,507
That's how it'll be.

628
00:22:29,429 --> 00:22:31,294
I'll win
the national tournament,

629
00:22:31,319 --> 00:22:32,989
and I'll go with Roberto
to Brazil

630
00:22:33,014 --> 00:22:34,684
to be a professional player.

631
00:22:36,463 --> 00:22:41,463
[ending theme]
